Parlay,X,offers,an,array,of,telephony,APIs,that,provide,services,such,as,managing,third,party,calls,sending,multimedia,messages,determining,user,location,and,providing,short,message,services,SMS,They,also,offer,APIs,for,managing,users,accounts,statuses,and,payments,The,Parlay,X,APIs,are,designed,to,enable,the,creation,of,telephony,applications,as,well,as,to,telecom,enable,IT,applications,These,APIs,are,intended,to,stimulate,the,development,of,network,applications,by,IT,developers,who,are,not,necessarily,experts,in,telephony,or,telecommunications